sentence: how many jamerican cuisine are there in santa cruz county ?
sentence-with-vars: how many VARrest are there in VARcounty ?
sql: select count(*) from RESTAURANT,GEOGRAPHIC where RESTAURANT.CITY_NAME=GEOGRAPHIC.CITY_NAME and GEOGRAPHIC.COUNTY='santa cruz county' and RESTAURANT.NAME='jamerican cuisine'
sql-with-vars: select count(*) from RESTAURANT,GEOGRAPHIC where RESTAURANT.CITY_NAME=GEOGRAPHIC.CITY_NAME and GEOGRAPHIC.COUNTY='VARcounty' and RESTAURANT.NAME='VARrest'
